New In! 🔥 Red Edition Challenger. 

A 1:16 scale beast designed with 738 pieces, custom race wheels, and a bold black hood that means business.

At its heart? A detailed V8 engine ready to rumble. Add in the pull-back motor and this muscle icon doesn’t just look fast — it is.

Slide it, launch it, admire it. The street legend is now in your hands.
